    "title": "Lead Investment Banker at Angel One",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Investment Banker with drive and ambition, Angel One in Nagpur is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Angel One:\nAngel One is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Angel One!",
